data.description: Welcome to this historic home built in 1888, located in the charming town of Leadville. This home has been remodeled with modern updates and offers a versatile floor plan with three bedrooms, an office and two bathrooms. Outside, you'll find a fenced in yard with two sheds to give you additional storage space. One of the standout features of this property is its prime location is walking distance to the historic main street. Don't miss this opportunity to won a piece of Leadville's history while enjoying the modern comforts of a thoughtfully remodeled home. With its desirable location and timeless charm, this property is sure to exceed your expectations.
